{"id":1221,"date":"2025-04-10T01:07:33","date_gmt":"2025-04-09T18:07:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1221"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:40:17","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:40:17","slug":"laser-nam","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/laser-nam\/","title":{"rendered":"Laser n\u00e1m"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u d\u00e0nh cho da n\u00e1m, t\u00e0n nhang, \u0111\u1ed3i m\u1ed3i&#8230;<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 melanin m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o melanin, ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da xung quanh.<\/li>\n<li>K\u00edch th\u00edch t\u0103ng sinh collagen, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da.<\/li>\n<li>Ra s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u sau m\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 laser s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00e1c t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00f3ng 532 &#8211; 755 &#8211; 1064nm, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ea5p thu t\u1ed1t b\u1edfi melanin t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da kh\u00e1c.<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba, l\u00e0m m\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da, duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng, m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn v\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c n\u00e1m v\u1edbi Tranexamic Acid 3%, 4-n-Butylresorcinol 1%, Alpha Arbutin 0.5%, Niacinamide 5%.<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ed9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi 3 in 1: Duy tr\u00ec &#8211; Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i &#8211; B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ~01 ti\u1ebfng (tu\u1ef3 v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eb9o).<\/li>\n<li>V\u1edbi li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<br \/>\nT\u00e0n nhang + \u0111\u1ed3i m\u1ed3i: 01 &#8211; 03 bu\u1ed5i, m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch nhau 01 th\u00e1ng.<br \/>\nN\u00e1m + t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1: 08 &#8211; 10 bu\u1ed5i t\u00f9y t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng, m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch nhau 07 &#8211; 10 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -3px; top: 93.3153px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u d\u00e0nh cho da n\u00e1m, t\u00e0n nhang, \u0111\u1ed3i m\u1ed3i,&#8230;<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3591,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[58],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1221","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-laser","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1221","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1221"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3591"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1221"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=1221"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=1221"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable"